snippet: A yacht and a dinghy crammed with immigrants trying to sneak into Greece capsized Monday, leaving at least 22 dead and several more missing in one of the deadliest accidents in Greek waters in recent years.
abstract: Yacht and a dinghy crammed with immigrants trying to sneak into Greece capsizes in the eastern Aegean Sea, leaving at least 22 dead and several more missing.
